								"__type" : "textStyle"
							},
							"string" : "**6. Executable proof over explanation:**   Prefer `<gtExample>` methods with assertions to demonstrate expected behavior."
						},
						{
							"__type" : "textSnippet",
							"children" : {
								"__type" : "snippets",
